POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classScheduleId": 5,
  "memberId": 6
}

### Test: Member with expired membership cannot book (Henry - member 8)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classScheduleId": 7,
  "memberId": 8
}

### Test: Freeze validation - too few days
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/memberships/3/freeze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "freezeDays": 3
}

### Test: Create member under 16 (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Young",
  "lastName": "Kid",
  "email": "young@example.com",
  "phone": "555-9999",
  "dateOfBirth": "2015-01-01",
  "emergencyContactName": "Parent",
  "emergencyContactPhone": "555-9998"
}
